A '''Cart00ney''' (usually spelled with two zeroes) is a [[neologism]] originallly coined in the [[Usenet]] [[newsgroup]] [[news.admin.net-abuse.email]] to describe both [[spammer]]s who threaten legal action to prohibit being described as spammers &mdash; for example, being added to [[blacklist]]s &mdash; as well as the threats themselves.

The use of the term is no longer restricted to spammers; it has expanded from its orignal meaning to include, for example, those who threaten [[Wikipedia]] administrators for taking action against them.

